      "message": "also, it clears d.additions and is idempotent. It is not obvious from this comment / function name. Same applies to delete and update.\n\nalternatively, the caller does not actually care about this behavior. add/delete/update functions could be simplified by doing a simple for loop over lists without making changes to struct fields",
